- The points \( x_0 \) and \( x_1 \).
- The predictor step as a solid blue arrow.
- The corrector step as a dotted blue arrow.
- The line segment \( s(t) \) connecting \( x_0 \) and \( x_1 \) as a thick red line.
- Tilted interval boxes centered along \( s(t) \).

